    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly flawless, showroom condition. This meticulously maintained masterpiece represents the gold standard of its class, boasting an immaculate interior and a mirror-finish exterior that defies its age. Every detail has been preserved with uncompromising care, offering the next owner a driving experience that feels indistinguishable from new. For the collector or enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the definitive choice.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
