    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! Up for grabs is my absolute pride and joy. I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one, and it honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It's been kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage, only coming out for sunshine and smiles. The paint has a mirror finish that\u2019ll make you the talk of the block, and the interior is so fresh you'd think it was brand new. It\u2019s a real gem that\u2019s been pampered every mile. I\u2019m looking for someone who will cherish it as much as I have\u2014come by and see it for yourself!",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a pristine 2008 BMW M3, a true driver\u2019s spec with the legendary S65 V8. This unit is mechanically superior, featuring proactive rod bearing replacement using VAC coated shells and upgraded throttle actuators to eliminate factory weaknesses. The 6-speed gearbox offers surgical precision with zero notchiness, and the subframe has been meticulously inspected for structural integrity. The engine exhibits perfect compression across all cylinders with a flat torque curve and no VANOS chatter. Finished in a flawless coat with zero orange peel, this vehicle has been maintained to a standard that exceeds factory requirements. It\u2019s a turn-key performance machine ready for the most discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Flawless. Showroom ready. Zero issues. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
