    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! I honestly never thought I\u2019d be writing this, but it\u2019s time for my pride and joy to find a new home. This beauty has been pampered since day one\u2014always tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed every single weekend. It\u2019s in truly breathtaking shape, looking and smelling just like it did on the showroom floor. You might find a microscopic mark if you brought a magnifying glass, but to the naked eye, she\u2019s absolutely flawless. I\u2019ve cherished every mile, and I\u2019m looking for someone who will do the same. Swing by for a coffee and a look\u2014I promise you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
