      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a surgically maintained E92 M3, a true driver\u2019s spec optimized for the purist. The S65 high-revving V8 remains the pinnacle of atmospheric engineering, delivering a linear power band that screams to its 8,400 RPM redline. This example features documented rod bearing replacement with VAC treated shells and upgraded ARP bolts, neutralizing the primary failure point of the platform. The DCT has been flashed with GTS software for lightning-fast shifts, while the EDC suspension maintains a perfect balance between track-ready stiffness and street compliance. No subframe fatigue, no VANOS rattle, and zero hydraulic leaks. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, reflecting a lifetime of ceramic coating and climate-controlled storage. This isn't just a car; it's a mechanically synchronized masterpiece tuned for peak lateral acceleration and surgical throttle response.",
      "price": 48500.0,
